    <section class="static-page__section">
        <h2>Using ToolNexus</h2>
        <p>You can use ToolNexus for personal or commercial work as long as it is legal and responsible. The platform is meant for productivity tasks like formatting, converting, and validating data.</p>
        <p>Please do not use the tools for abuse, scraping attacks, malware workflows, or anything that can hurt other users or the platform.</p>
